
@{
    ViewBag.Title = "About";
}

<style>
    .about-page h2, .about-page h3 {
        color: #007bff;
    }

    .about-page p, .about-page li {
        color: #555;
    }

    .about-page ul {
        list-style-type: none;
        padding-left: 0;
    }

    .about-page ul li::before {
        content: "\2022";
        color: #007bff;
        font-weight: bold;
        display: inline-block;
        width: 1em;
        margin-left: -1em;
    }

    .about-page .container {
        margin-top: 2rem;
    }

    .about-page .lead {
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        font-weight: 300;
    }

    .about-page .values-list {
        padding-left: 0;
    }

    .about-page .values-list li {
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
</style>

<h2>About</h2>

<div class="container about-page">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-8">
            <h3>Our Story</h3>
            <p class="lead">
                Welcome to Capemint Holdings, a leading company in the hospitality industry dedicated to providing exceptional experiences to our guests. Our journey began with a simple vision: to create a place where comfort, luxury, and unforgettable memories come together.
            </p>
            <p>
                Founded in 2024, Capemint Holdings has grown from a small, family-run business to a renowned name in the industry. Our commitment to excellence and our passion for hospitality have been the driving forces behind our success.
            </p>
            <h3>Our Mission</h3>
            <p>
                At Capemint Holdings, our mission is to deliver unparalleled hospitality services that exceed our guests' expectations. We believe in creating an environment where every guest feels valued and appreciated. Our dedicated team works tirelessly to ensure that every stay is a memorable one.
            </p>
            <h3>Our Values</h3>
            <ul class="values-list">
                <li><strong>Integrity:</strong> We operate with honesty and transparency in everything we do.</li>
                <li><strong>Excellence:</strong> We strive for perfection in all our services and facilities.</li>
                <li><strong>Innovation:</strong> We continuously seek new ways to enhance the guest experience.</li>
                <li><strong>Respect:</strong> We treat our guests, employees, and partners with the utmost respect.</li>
                <li><strong>Sustainability:</strong> We are committed to sustainable practices that protect our planet.</li>
            </ul>
            <h3>Our Future</h3>
            <p>
                As we look to the future, Capemint Holdings is poised for continued growth and success. We are excited to expand our portfolio and introduce new and innovative hospitality solutions. Our focus remains on providing exceptional value and experiences to our guests, ensuring that Capemint Holdings remains a name synonymous with excellence.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

